{"lastUpdated":"2026-06-16T19:13:32.459Z","seriesId":523343,"title":"映像版マンガ日本史","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45169066/45169066.16655846","descriptionFirst":"「謎のベールに包まれた女王とそこから始まる日本の物語」古代日本の女王“卑弥呼”の伝説を映像化（朝日新聞出版　週刊マンガ日本史０１号より）。卑弥呼は古代日本の女王で、倭国の統一を目指し外交にも優れた才能を持つ。彼女は神聖な存在とされ、美貌と知恵で多くの人々を魅了したと言われる。後世に語り継がれた伝説の一部を物語で表現。当映像はライトアニメの手法を活用し制作。\n\n制作:大日本印刷株式会社／底本刊行:朝日新聞出版\n\n©STUDIO 2B/Asahi Shimbun Publications Inc. /Dai Nippon Printing Co., Ltd.\n\n次話→so45169071","tags":["アニメ","第一話","大日本印刷","OVA/OAD/TVSP/TV未放送","歴史/戦記"],"cours":null,"colKey":"ま","relatedSeries":[{"seriesId":480454,"title":"0歳児スタートダッシュ物語","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/43942270/43942270.53076582"}],"episodes":[{"contentId":"so45169070","episodeNo":1,"title":"映像版マンガ日本史　第1話　卑弥呼","viewCounter":292,"startTime":"2025-08-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45169070/45169070.26650927"},{"contentId":"so45169071","episodeNo":2,"title":"映像版マンガ日本史　第2話　聖徳太子","viewCounter":68,"startTime":"2025-08-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45169071/45169071.51875522"},{"contentId":"so45169072","episodeNo":3,"title":"映像版マンガ日本史　第3話　坂上田村麻呂","viewCounter":44,"startTime":"2025-08-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45169072/45169072.50682807"},{"contentId":"so45169073","episodeNo":4,"title":"映像版マンガ日本史　第4話　安倍晴明","viewCounter":28,"startTime":"2025-08-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45169073/45169073.78866866"},{"contentId":"so45169074","episodeNo":5,"title":"映像版マンガ日本史　第5話　源頼朝","viewCounter":35,"startTime":"2025-08-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45169074/45169074.56515691"},{"contentId":"so45169075","episodeNo":6,"title":"映像版マンガ日本史　第6話　足利尊氏","viewCounter":30,"startTime":"2025-08-01T00:00:00+09:00","thumbnailUrl":"https://nicovideo.cdn.nimg.jp/thumbnails/45169075/45169075.6148424